Flying saucer



This was another large balloon in the shape of a flying saucer, tethered close to the ground. This shot is looking in through its opening, where the wind entered to keep it inflated.
Taken Sunday, February 08, 2004, 03:22:59pm.  Original image size: 3072x2048, 5.5Mb
Technical details: Canon EOS D60, 1/200s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 70-200mm/F2.8+1.4x @ 255mm (408mm equiv)
